## Error Handling

| Scenario | Handling |
|----------|---------|
| Git clone fails (invalid URL, auth failure, repo not found) | Deployment marked `FAILED` with error message. Build directory cleaned up. |
| No framework detected and no `deploy.yaml` | `detectFramework()` throws; deployment marked `FAILED`. |
| Dependency install fails (`pnpm install` exits non-zero) | Deployment marked `FAILED` with stderr output. |
| Build command fails (`pnpm build` exits non-zero) | Deployment marked `FAILED` with stderr output. |
| Docker image build fails | Deployment marked `FAILED` with Docker error message. |
| Build timeout (15 minutes) | All child processes killed via AbortController. Deployment marked `FAILED`. |
| S3 cache restore fails | Non-fatal. Warning logged. Build continues without cache. |
| S3 cache save fails | Non-fatal. Warning logged. Build result is still valid. |
| Database update fails | Error logged. The build result is still valid but the deployment record may be stale. |
| Project not found in database | Throws immediately. Build does not start. |

